<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Guidelines</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Guidelines.css">
    <!-- Google Fonts for a clean, modern look -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- ScrollReveal CDN for scroll animations -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/scrollreveal"></script>
</head>
<body>
    
    <div id="main">
        <!-- Sticky Header -->
        <div id="header">
            <div class="logo">College Dost</div>    
            <div class="Guideline"><h1>Guidelines</h1></div>
            <div class="box">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">Home</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Fake Header to push content below the fixed header -->
        <div id="fakeheader"></div>

        <!-- Main Content Area -->
        <div id="page1">
            <div class="content-container">
                <h3 class="reveal-title">To maintain a healthy and respectful environment, all users must follow these guidelines:</h3>

                <ul class="guidelines-list">
                    <li class="reveal-item">Respect all users and mentors.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Avoid sharing offensive, abusive, or harmful content.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Do not misuse the anonymous chat feature.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Follow academic integrity and honesty.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Mentors should provide genuine and helpful guidance.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Do not share personal contact details (phone number, address, etc.) publicly.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Avoid spamming messages or sending repeated content.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Do not share false or misleading information.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Use the platform only for educational and guidance purposes.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Maintain polite and professional communication.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Do not impersonate another user or mentor.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Report any inappropriate behavior to the admin.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Do not upload or share copyrighted or illegal content.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Respect privacy of other users at all times.</li>
                    <li class="reveal-item">Use appropriate language in chats and posts.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="page2">
             <!-- Ready for any extra content or footer structures -->
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Link to your JavaScript interactions -->
    <script src="/js/Guidelines.js"></script>
</body>
</html>